"\"<b><font size=\\\"5\\\">&nbsp;WHAT PARTICIPANTS WILL LEARN<\/font><\/b><div><span style=\\\"background-color: rgb(243 244 246 \/ var(--tw-bg-opacity));\\\"><br><\/span><\/div><div><span style=\\\"background-color: rgb(243 244 246 \/ var(--tw-bg-opacity));\\\">The Mindful leadership workshop is designed to:&nbsp;<\/span><br><\/div><div>&nbsp;\u25cf understand the psychological makeup of the leader&nbsp;<\/div><div>&nbsp;\u25cf improve mental focus and reduce spacing out when stressed out&nbsp;<\/div><div>&nbsp;\u25cf assist in staying organized, managing time, and setting priorities&nbsp;<\/div><div>&nbsp;\u25cf Improve level of adversity and gratitude quotient&nbsp;<\/div><div>&nbsp;\u25cf optimization of attitude and emotional intelligence&nbsp;<\/div><div>&nbsp;\u25cf integration into every domain of daily life, work, and relationships<br><\/div><div><br><\/div><div><b><font size=\\\"5\\\">COURSE DETAILS<\/font><\/b><\/div><div><br><\/div><div>Training Agenda:<\/div><div><b>\u25cf MODULE 1:<\/b> Understanding Knowledge, Attitude, Skills&nbsp;<\/div><div><b>\u25cf MODULE 2: <\/b>Leadership presence and impact in the organization&nbsp;<\/div><div><b>\u25cf MODULE 3:<\/b> Eustress VS Distress&nbsp;<\/div><div><b>\u25cf MODULE 4: <\/b>Mindfulness skills building&nbsp;<\/div><div><b>\u25cf MODULE 5: <\/b>Adversity quotient&nbsp;<\/div><div><b>\u25cf MODULE 6: <\/b>Gratitude quotient<br><\/div>\""